short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tel Aviv university autofill addon for Moodle and tau site

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This addon autofill your ID section when you enter Moodle or Tau. 

After downloading the addon you have to enter your ID via the plugin popup, after that your ID will autofill every time you enter one of websites above.
